data.description: Now Complete!  New construction on Lot 1 Phase 2 Talon Pointe at South Mountain. Four bedroom two bath home with a great open floor plan, kitchen with white cabinets and gorgeous back splash, front yard landscaping included. Large pantry and mudroom. Custom cabinets, upgraded laminate flooring throughout the main living area, carpet in the bedrooms, extended back patio!
